===Noun===
''[[conga]] [[line]]'''
# A dance where people are in a line, one behind the other grabbing onto the person in front's hips and the people take three small steps forward and then kick out with their leg on the fourth beat, and they as a chain of people weave about the place, picking up people who go to the back of the line and join them in their routine. 

